                "key": "Halcyon Years Unending",
                "string_values": [
                  "<p>Gain \"Ode to Flowers\" after Normal or Plunging Attacks hit an opponent: DEF increases by <span style=\"color: rgb(55, 255, 255)\">8%/10%/12%/14%/16%</span> and gain a <span style=\"color: rgb(55, 255, 255)\">10%/12.5%/15%/17.5%/20%</span> All Elemental DMG Bonus for 6s. Max 2 stacks. Can trigger once per 0.1s. When this effect reaches 2 stacks or the 2nd stack's duration is refreshed, increase all nearby party members' All Elemental DMG Bonus by <span style=\"color: #37FFFF\">8%/10%/12%/14%/16%</span> for every 1,000 DEF the equipping character has, up to a maximum of <span style=\"color: rgb(55, 255, 255)\">25.6%/32%/38.4%/44.8%/51.2%</span>, for 15s.</p>"
                ]
              },
